&lt;p&gt;Hello and welcome to my slice of the internet !&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who am I ?&lt;/strong&gt;   My name is reformer-zero and I consider myself a lifelong learner. I created this website (with the help of existing technologies - check the site footer for proper attribution) to host all the links that make up my digital identity  and to store and share knowledge and reflections. Additionally, I imagine that the exposure of my writing to the  public might provide a good rationale for maintaining a high level of quality and consistency.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
